Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [telegram] <freerider101> pow algos have nothing to do with atomic swap ability (re @tim87: how does atomic swaps inside komodo work if coins use different algos etc)

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [telegram] <freerider101> To perform an atomic swap, both assets are locked up in a 2-of-2 multisig address (with a timeout that allows the original owner to reclaim it). At least one of the two networks has to support Schnorr signatures (preferably both).
